# PGOPDeployer Smart Contract (v0.2)

This contract powers the on-chain plugin and contributor registry for the **Pretty Good OSINT Protocol (PGOP)**.

## 🔐 Key Features

- Contributor registration (by approved contributors)
- Plugin registration with metadata and approval
- Publicly accessible verification system for plugin hashes

